title: No evidence of FBI spy in Trump campaign: Dems
text:
No evidence of FBI spy in Trump campaign: Dems 2:19am IST - 00:30
Adam Schiff, the top Democrat on the House Intelligence Committee, says nothing Democratic lawmakers heard in classified briefings on the FBI probe into Russian election meddling changed their view that there is no evidence to support President Trump's claim that the FBI planted a spy in his campaign.
